 《全面战争：战锤 3》补丁删除了随机生成的与纳粹有关的名字https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-removes-nazi-name-3603409?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=total-war-warhammer-3-removes-nazi-姓名Issy van der VeldeTue, 19 Mar 2024 13:59:10 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3603409 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《全面战争：战锤 3》、《变革之影》。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>多么不幸的巧合</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-removes-nazi-name-3603409">《全面战争：战锤 3》后补丁剪切了随机生成的与纳粹有联系的名字，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《全面战争：战锤 3》、《变革之影》。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Total-War-Warhammer-3-Shadows-Of-Change-Yuan-Bo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war-warhammer-3"><em>《全面战争：战锤 3》</em></a>刚刚推出了一个新的修补程序，其中删除了一个随机生成的高等精灵名字，该名字与第二次世界大战中的一位德国将军有联系。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/how-total-war-warhammer-3-carved-out-an-empire-3353623">《全面战争：战锤 3》如何打造一个帝国</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>随机生成的高等精灵名字之一“古德里安”是纳粹将军海因茨·古德里安的姓氏。他率领装甲师进入波兰、法国和俄罗斯，是德国在第二次世界大战中用来迅速压倒其他国家的臭名昭著的闪电战战术的早期先驱。</p><p>古德里安升任希特勒的私人顾问，但他最终于 1945 年向美军投降，一直被监禁至 1948 年，并于 1956 年去世。</p><p>可以理解的是， <em>《全面战争》</em>团队不希望他们的任何角色与纳粹联系在一起，因此他们在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war-warhammer-2">《战锤 2》</a></em>和<em>《战锤 3》</em>中删除了这个名字。该团队写道：“最近我们了解到，高等精灵池中随机生成的一个名字可能与 20 世纪历史上的一个可恶角色有关。 </p><figure id="attachment_3353698" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3353698" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3353698" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires.jpg" alt="《全面战争：战锤 3》。图片来源：Creative Assembly。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Warhammer-3-immortal-empires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3353698" class="wp-caption-text"> 《全面战争：战锤 3》。图片来源：Creative Assembly。</figcaption></figure><p> “我们对这个名字在游戏中出现这么久表示歉意，并感谢那些提请我们注意的人，以便我们采取行动。”</p><p>除了从<em>《全面战争》</em>中删除问题名称之外，团队还为游戏添加了一些错误修复和视觉调整。 Saytang 进行了一些视觉上的改变，以确保传说的真实性。许多英雄已将他们的突击部队更改为突击部队，现在对敌方军队中的随机单位造成伤害。弗拉德和伊莎贝拉·冯·卡斯坦因现在可以正确侦察废墟。最后，在格罗布林达尔的任务战斗“朱夫巴尔的符文头盔”的介绍过场动画中，镜头不应再夹入地形。</p><p> <a href="https://community.creative-assembly.com/total-war/total-war-warhammer/forums/7-patch-notes-amp-announcements/threads/3973" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请在此处阅读完整的补丁说明</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/stardew-valley-new-farm-3603289"><em>星露谷物语</em>正在获得一种新的农场类型</a>，这可能会严重改变速通玩家玩舒适的农场模拟器的方式。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-removes-nazi-name-3603409">《全面战争：战锤 3》后补丁剪切了随机生成的与纳粹有联系的名字，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
