ews/music/deep-purple-hostile-police-incident-smoke-on-the-water-3412407">谈到了他们在录制“Smoke on the Water”时与瑞士警方发生的事件</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deep-purple-announce-one-more-time-uk-tour-with-reef-buy-tickets-3603449">Deep Purple 宣布与 Reef 进行“One More Time”英国巡演的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
